explains: v. 解释，说明；口译；把……理解为；演绎

sentences.en: The students were asked to interpret the poem.
sentences.cn: 学生们被要求诠释那首诗的意义。

sentences.en: The data is hard to interpret than I expected.
sentences.cn: 解读这些数据比我预期的要难。

sentences.en: Historians annotate, check and interpret the diary selections.
sentences.cn: 历史学家们对这些日记选段进行注释、核对和阐释。
